text: Tetsumi Nabeya (born 2 January 1930) is a Japanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
